&lt;li&gt;Determining whether issues originate from software logic, communication protocols, configuration mismatches, or physical hardware defects&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Performing deep-dive diagnostics including timing analysis, plausibility checks, and state transition reviews across ECUs, sensors, and actuators&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Reproducing complex issues on real vehicles and capturing ECU, network, and system-level logs to document findings&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Driving structured root cause investigations using data, instrumentation, and experimentation&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Driving fast, high-quality technical decision making in ambiguous and time-sensitive situations&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Triaging complex issues and coordinating resolution across service and engineering teams&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Contributing to validation strategies including bench testing, HIL, and production-level verification&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborating with engineering and production teams to implement improvements to boat designs, production methods, and service processes&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Improving system reliability, diagnosability, and serviceability across product iterations&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Contributing to technical problem solving, design reviews, and cross-functional debugging efforts with engineering teams&lt;/li&gt;
